Dialogue: 1,0:24:47.04,0:24:50.04,0wrt,F,0,0,0,,{\1c091414\3c091414\b1\bord0.2\pos(461.667,538.934)}與\N山\N以\N彩\N裳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.79,0:24:51.41,2prop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,651)}Grazie
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.79,0:24:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:52.29,2prop,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,651)}Grazie
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.25,0:24:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要踩了  要踩了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.04,0:24:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥遜爆了
