Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:51.81,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}華麗的裝飾也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:53.52,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}都不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:55.57,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}桌上的飯菜也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:57.36,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨天的錯誤也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:59.20,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不安的明天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:00.36,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}全部加上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:02.87,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吶  就算什麼都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:04.74,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凍僵的腳步也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:06.62,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}精美的裝盤也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.33,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}都不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.58,0:24:10.33,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}眼淚的味道也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:12.13,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算是咸咸的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:14.13,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}最後也會一直
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.17,0:24:17.51,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.71,0:24:20.80,edcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這就是調味品

